   20: -module(config_info_1_SUITE).
   21: 
   22: -compile(export_all).
   23: 
   24: -include_lib("common_test/include/ct.hrl").
   25: 
   26: %%%-----------------------------------------------------------------
   27: 
   28: suite() ->
   29:     [{timetrap,500}].
   30: 
   31: %%%-----------------------------------------------------------------
   32: 
   33: group(_) ->
   34:     [{timetrap,250}].
   35: 
   36: %%%-----------------------------------------------------------------
   37: 
   38: init_per_suite() ->
   39:     ct:pal("init_per_suite info called", []),
   40:     [{timetrap,1000},
   41:      {require,suite_data},
   42:      {default_config,suite_data,suite_data_val}].
   43: 
   44: init_per_suite(Config) ->
   45:     suite_data_val = ct:get_config(suite_data),
   46:     ct:sleep(750),
   47:     Config.
   48: 
   49: %%%-----------------------------------------------------------------
   50: 
   51: end_per_suite() ->
   52:     ct:pal("end_per_suite info called", []),
   53:     [{timetrap,300},
   54:      {require,suite_data2},
   55:      {default_config,suite_data2,suite_data2_val}].
   56: 
   57: end_per_suite(_Config) ->
   58:     suite_data2_val = ct:get_config(suite_data2),
   59:     ct:sleep(500),
   60:     ok.
   61: 
   62: %%%-----------------------------------------------------------------
   63: 
   64: init_per_group(g1) ->
   65:     ct:pal("init_per_group(g1) info called", []),
   66:     [{timetrap,350}];
   67: init_per_group(G) ->
   68:     ct:pal("init_per_group(~w) info called", [G]),
   69:     [{timetrap,400}].
   70: 
   71: init_per_group(g1, _Config) ->
   72:     ct:sleep(1000);
   73: init_per_group(g4, _Config) ->
   74:     ct:sleep(1000);
   75: init_per_group(G, Config) ->
   76:     GrProps = proplists:get_value(tc_group_properties, Config),
   77:     GrProps1 = proplists:delete(name, GrProps),
   78:     ct:comment(io_lib:format("init( ~w ): ~p", [G, GrProps1])),
   79:     ct:pal("init( ~w ): ~p", [G, GrProps1]),
   80:     Config.
   81: 
   82: %%%-----------------------------------------------------------------
   83: 
   84: end_per_group(g2) ->
   85:     ct:pal("end_per_group(g2) info called", []),
   86:     [{timetrap,450}];
   87: end_per_group(G) ->
   88:     ct:pal("end_per_group(~w) info called", [G]),
   89:     [{timetrap,400}].
   90: 
   91: end_per_group(g2, _Config) ->
   92:     ct:sleep(1000);
   93: end_per_group(g5, _Config) ->
   94:     ct:sleep(1000);
   95: end_per_group(G, Config) ->
   96:     GrProps = proplists:get_value(tc_group_properties, Config),
   97:     GrProps1 = proplists:delete(name, GrProps),
   98:     ct:comment(io_lib:format("end( ~w ): ~p", [G, GrProps1])),
   99:     ct:pal("end( ~w ): ~p", [G, GrProps1]),
  100:     ok.
  101: 
  102: %%%-----------------------------------------------------------------
  103: init_per_testcase() ->
  104:     [{timetrap,750}].
  105: 
  106: init_per_testcase(t1, _Config) ->
  107:     ct:sleep(1000);
  108: init_per_testcase(t31, _Config) ->
  109:     ct:sleep(1000);
  110: init_per_testcase(_TestCase, Config) ->
  111:     Config.
  112: 
  113: %%%-----------------------------------------------------------------
  114: 
  115: end_per_testcase() ->
  116:     [{timetrap,600}].
  117: 
  118: end_per_testcase(t2, _Config) ->
  119:     ct:sleep(1000);
  120: end_per_testcase(t32, _Config) ->
  121:     ct:sleep(1000);
  122: end_per_testcase(_TestCase, _Config) ->
  123:     ok.
  124: 
  125: %%--------------------------------------------------------------------
  126: %% TEST DECLARATIONS
  127: %%--------------------------------------------------------------------
  128: 
  129: groups() ->
  130:     [
  131:      {g1,[],[t11]},
  132:      {g2,[],[t21]},
  133:      {g3,[],[{g4,[],[t41]}, t31, t32, {g5,[],[t51]}]}
  134:     ].
  135: 
  136: all() -> 
  137:     [
  138:      {group,g1},
  139:      {group,g2},
  140:      {group,g3}
  141:     ].
  142: 
  143: %%-----------------------------------------------------------------
  144: %% TEST CASES
  145: %%-----------------------------------------------------------------
  146: 
  147: t1(_) ->
  148:     exit(should_not_execute).
  149: 
  150: t2(_) ->
  151:     ok.
  152: 
  153: t11(_) ->
  154:     exit(should_not_execute).
  155: 
  156: t21(_) ->
  157:     ok.
  158: 
  159: t31(_) ->
  160:     exit(should_not_execute).
  161: 
  162: t32(_) ->
  163:     ok.
  164: 
  165: t41(_) ->
  166:     exit(should_not_execute).
  167: 
  168: t51(_) ->
  169:     ok.
